				<td colspan="2"><span>I'm just learning how to AoE kite as well and I used the guide written by Reinhard to help me get started.  
<br />

<br />
http://www.eqdiva.com/EQ/Guide.aspx?id=27&amp;ForumID=132
<br />

<br />
I'm level 14 now and have been using his strats since level 3 and I'd have to say that they are very effective.  There are a few other, well written, guides detailing how to kite and what not in the Guides section of this forum you should check them out.
<br />

<br />
Also, if you don't mind me asking.  What've you been doing for 50 levels to not have used AoE kiting?  It was one of the first things I learned to do when I mem'd my Chord of Dissonace song.  Anyway, as a warning, it takes alot of practice to get it down and definitely alot of deaths as well but, its a great way to get tons of xp once you've mastered it.
<br />

<br />
Moezart
<br />
14th Half Elf Bard
